    "description": {
      "value": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid;\">By 18th level, you can call in a 2m tall by 1m wide supply pylon to a location within 4m. At the start of your next turn, the pylon arrives. If any creature is standing in the targeted location, the creature must make a Dexterity saving throw with advantage. On a failed save, a creature takes 4d8 bludgeoning damage and is knocked prone.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid; text-indent: 1em;\">The pylon contains 5 resources from the following list, which you choose when you call the pylon:</p>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: -0.5em; padding-left: 1em; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside none; text-indent: -1em;\">\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: -0.5em; padding-left: 1em; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside none; text-indent: -1em;\">\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; padding-left: 1.4em; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside disc; text-indent: 0px;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\">1 heavy weapon ammo charges</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\">10 thermal clips</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\">A battery capable to quickly recharging your Omni-tool, recovering 5 tech points</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\">A stim pack capable of staving off biotic fatigue, recovering 5 levels worth of spell slots</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\">4 enhanced medi-gel</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\">2 Mk II Frag grenades</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\">2 Mk II Lift Grenades</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\">2 Mk IV Flashbang</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\">2 Mk IV Smoke grenades</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid; text-indent: 1em;\">Once the pylon has landed, friendly creatures (including you) within melee range of the pylon can use their action to collect one of the resources you chose.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid; text-indent: 1em;\">Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest and restock the pylon with 5 omni-gel.</p>",
